<section class="grfacts"><div class="wrapper"><div class="fact"><div class="text long"><h2>Grand River Facts</h2>
						GRH has improved emergency department length of stay by 12 per cent while seeing a nine per cent increase in volumes. More than 65,000 emergency patients are treated at GRH every year.
